Falcon Cable Systems Co, de say e propose one amendment wey go allow am increase en debt to 65% of di company price from di 40% wey dey allow am now.

Falkon, one limited partnership, e say e wan add money to continue im $2.15 per unit monthly, and for expansion, and acquisition.

One spokesman for di company yarn sey dem go do one meeting for shareholders wey go vote on top di amendment before di year end.

